Food hall

Quick, fresh, and flavorful dishes inspired by street food from around the world. Enjoy favorites like poké bowls and Pad Kra Pao chicken – and for sausage lovers, Wurst Case Scenario serves up juicy, flavorful sausages with creative toppings and vegetarian options. Perfect when you want something fast, light, and packed with taste.

Opening hours

Two worlds of flavor

The Food Hall brings together two exciting concepts, offering a diverse mix of flavors and experiences. Enjoy vibrant Pan-Asian street food with fresh noodles, ramen, baos, and Bánh Mì, alongside gourmet sausages with bold toppings and plenty of variety, including vegetarian options. Whether you’re after something quick, light, or indulgent, there’s always a taste to match your craving.

Bao Bao

Pan-Asian street food with a focus on fresh flavors and simple, vibrant dishes. Enjoy noodles, ramen, baos, and Bánh Mì – flavorful creations inspired by Asian street food, served with a clean and modern twist.

Wurst Case Scenario

Sausages at their best, made with 85–95% meat content, exciting toppings, and bold flavors. The menu offers plenty of variety, including vegetarian options and quick service – perfect for a standing lunch, a quick bite, or doubling up for extra indulgence.

Hantera samtycke
För att ge en bra upplevelse använder vi teknik som cookies för att lagra och/eller komma åt enhetsinformation. När du samtycker till dessa tekniker kan vi behandla data som surfbeteende eller unika ID:n på denna webbplats. Om du inte samtycker eller om du återkallar ditt samtycke kan detta påverka vissa funktioner negativt.
Funktionell Alltid aktiv

Alternativ

Statistik
